The demonstration programs are

list_class --

	A very simple "list" class.  Documentation is included in
	LaTeX format in the file list_class.tex

color_chooser --

	Simple graphical "color chooser" program.  Documentation is
	included in LaTeX form in the file color_chooser.tex

	This directory's Makefile builds the 'demo' program.  You may
	need to specify other values for CC or include paths, specific
	to your system.

word_bfs --

	Simple shortest-path graph searching program.  Documentation
	in the Prolog source: word_bfs.pl, word_obj.pl, word_sgb.pl

	The sample data in word_sgb.pl has no Objects dependencies.
	Use it to compare your own shortest-path programs to the
	sample program

